# Keep scripts, workflow YAML, and Dockerfiles as LF regardless of the OS they
# were committed from — the deploy runs them on the Linux host, where CRLF
# would break shebangs and the deploy.yml run-block. (These are already LF in
# the repo, so this pins the behavior without a renormalization diff.)
*.sh    text eol=lf
*.yml   text eol=lf
*.yaml  text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf

# Never touch binary assets.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico  binary
